{"tid":700093,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"金仔帶私家馬桶，防糞便被偷。","createTime":"2018-06-13T05:23:38.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-13T05:40:08.000Z","uid":31208,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"edc9519b590781f2e00847b93ace591715253369","tid":700093,"uid":31208,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T05:23:38.000Z","msg":"帶私家馬桶　防糞便被偷<br />\n<br />\n特朗普與金正恩的「世紀握手」亦成為社交網站焦點，有好事網民製作改圖，把二人標誌性的經典髮型對調，戲稱這是「獨裁者的髮型對決」，又為他們配上惡搞對白，猜想他們會互相指罵對方的髮型醜陋。<br />\n另外，金正恩這次到新加坡，據報跟上次到南韓出席峯會一樣，攜帶了數個私家馬桶，其中一個在他的平治房車上，以免糞便外洩使健康資訊曝光。據報已故中國領導人毛澤東就被前蘇聯取得他的糞便，蘇共領袖史太林從中分析毛的健康狀況後，拒絕簽署當時談判的協議，因此北韓的憂慮不無道理。<br />\n南韓《韓國時報》/英國《每日郵報》"},{"pid":"7af2c14c84f70a7b24f5d39a547b01ad3b62b81f","tid":700093,"uid":2419,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T05:27:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bbb16e1e913cc81294541c0e63d0fe73528a7336","tid":700093,"uid":148652,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T05:29:44.000Z","msg":"間諜世界咩都有可能，分分鐘你簽完名支筆都可以拎黎做DNA化驗"},{"pid":"efbadb9ce7e3d4875618a466d38e9295d10a4805","tid":700093,"uid":72831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T05:30:17.000Z","msg":"偷屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eca2bb9d71d36f14e2e00e796a67b3d33e720bdf","tid":700093,"uid":41292,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T05:30:22.000Z","msg":"屎太淋 唔簽"},{"pid":"eeafc83bdf9c5eac90f9e3e03d7deaef8720c7f5","tid":700093,"uid":33875,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T05:34:02.000Z","msg":"要帶埋私家雞"},{"pid":"0d6077e6a6465d2c497e91b9cdd1eb448a26be6c","tid":700093,"uid":69568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"eca2bb9d71d36f14e2e00e796a67b3d33e720bdf","tid":700093,"uid":41292,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T05:30:22.000Z","msg":"屎太淋 唔簽"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T05:40:08.00